channel.title: When using Reflection (Help)
channel.description: Ok so, so you use reflection you get it started up & all with the rsps. You try to enter something on the cheat pannel like "noclip" & it doesn't enter or go thorugh what does that mean, it doesn't work for that rsps? I've tryed it before on the rsps & it worked before. Is there anyway to get around this & get it to go through the cheat pannel?

item.title: When using Reflection (Help)
item.dc:creator: @ohokay ohokay
item.description:
@ohokay wrote:

Either the code for noclip is wrong, or the server has clipping, which doesn’t allow you to noclip.
